    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="356468698">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-356468698" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-356468698" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="356468698">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/flower1218/">大地繁花</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-12-17</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">冬日的南方，漫长的旅途，终于看完了这本书。翔实的数据，磨难的现实比电影更残酷。书中未经粉饰的辛德勒，比电影更真实。一个有着大缺点的男性商人，在乱世中被激发出全部机智，散发人性光辉。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1013933612">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1013933612" class="vote-count">0</span>
